ductions Inc.}}</ref>\n\n{{Track listing\n| extra_column    = Producer(s)\n\n| title1          = [[Jam (song)|Jam]]\n| writer1         = {{hlist|[[Michael Jackson]]|[[Ren\u00e9 Moore]]|[[Bruce Swedien]]|[[Teddy Riley]]}}\n| extra1          = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley|Swedien}}\n| length1         = 5:39\n\n| title2          = Why You Wanna Trip on Me\n| writer2         = {{hlist|Riley|[[Bernard Belle]]}}\n| extra2          = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley}}\n| length2         = 5:24\n\n| title3          = [[In the Closet]]\n| writer3         = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley}}\n| extra3          = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley}}\n| length3         = 6:32\n\n| title4          = She Drives Me Wild\n| writer4         = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley|[[Wreckx-n-Effect|Aqil Davidson]]}}\n| extra4          = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley}}\n| length4         = 3:42\n\n| title5          = [[Remember the Time]]\n| writer5         = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley|Belle}}\n| extra5          = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley}}\n| length5         = 4:01\n\n| title6          = [[Can't Let Her Get Away]]\n| writer6         = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley}}\n| extra6          = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley}}\n| length6         = 4:59\n\n| title7          = [[Heal the World]]\n| writer7         = {{hlist|Jackson}}\n| extra7          = {{hlist|Jackson|Swedien}}\n| length7         = 6:25\n\n| title8          = [[Black or White]]\n| writer8         = {{hlist|Jackson|[[Bill Bottrell]]}}\n| extra8          = {{hlist|Jackson|Bottrell}}\n| length8         = 4:16\n\n| title9          = [[Who Is It (Michael Jackson song)|Who Is It]]\n| writer9         = Jackson\n| extra9          = {{hlist|Jackson|Bottrell}} \n| length9         = 6:35\n\n| title10         = [[Give In to Me]]\n| writer10        = {{hlist|Jackson|Bottrell}}\n| extra10         = {{hlist|Jackson|Bottrell}}\n| length10        = 5:30\n\n| title11         = [[Will You Be There]]\n| writer11        = {{hlist|Jackson}}\n| extra11         = {{hlist|Jackson|Swedien}}\n| length11        = 7:41\n\n| title12         = 