vidson]]}}\n| extra4          = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley}}\n| length4         = 3:42\n\n| title5          = [[Remember the Time]]\n| writer5         = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley|Belle}}\n| extra5          = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley}}\n| length5         = 4:01\n\n| title6          = [[Can't Let Her Get Away]]\n| writer6         = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley}}\n| extra6          = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley}}\n| length6         = 4:59\n\n| title7          = [[Heal the World]]\n| writer7         = {{hlist|Jackson}}\n| extra7          = {{hlist|Jackson|Swedien}}\n| length7         = 6:25\n\n| title8          = [[Black or White]]\n| writer8         = {{hlist|Jackson|[[Bill Bottrell]]}}\n| extra8          = {{hlist|Jackson|Bottrell}}\n| length8         = 4:16\n\n| title9          = [[Who Is It (Michael Jackson song)|Who Is It]]\n| writer9         = Jackson\n| extra9          = {{hlist|Jackson|Bottrell}} \n| length9         = 6:35\n\n| title10         = [[Give In to Me]]\n| writer10        = {{hlist|Jackson|Bottrell}}\n| extra10         = {{hlist|Jackson|Bottrell}}\n| length10        = 5:30\n\n| title11         = [[Will You Be There]]\n| writer11        = {{hlist|Jackson}}\n| extra11         = {{hlist|Jackson|Swedien}}\n| length11        = 7:41\n\n| title12         = Keep the Faith\n| writer12        = {{hlist|Jackson|[[Glen Ballard]]|[[Siedah Garrett]]}}\n| extra12         = {{hlist|Jackson|Swedien}}\n| length12        = 5:57\n\n| title13         = [[Gone Too Soon]]\n| writer13        = {{hlist|[[Larry Grossman (composer)|Larry Grossman]]|[[Buz Kohan]]}}\n| extra13         = {{hlist|Jackson|Swedien}}\n| length13        = 3:22\n\n| title14         = [[Dangerous (Michael Jackson song)|Dangerous]]\n| writer14        = {{hlist|Jackson|Bottrell|Riley}}\n| extra14         = {{hlist|Jackson|Riley}}\n| length14        = 6:57\n\n| total_length = 77:03\n}}\n\n== Personnel ==\nPersonnel as listed in the album's [[liner notes]].<ref>{{cite AV media notes|title= Dangerous |year= 1991 |type= booklet |publisher= [[Epic Records]]}}</ref>\n{{div col||colwidth=30em}}\n* [[John Bahler]] \u2013 vocal and choir arrangements {{small|(track 7)}}\n* The John Bahler Singers \u2013 choir {{small|(track 7)}}\n* [[Glen Ballard]] \u2013 arrangements {{small|(track 12)}}\n* John Barnes \u2013 keyboards {{small|(track 8)}}\n* [[Michael Boddicker]] \u2013 synthesizer {{small|(tracks 1, 7, 11\u201313)}}, sequencer {{small|(8)}}, keyboards and programming {{small|(9)}}\n* [[Bill Bottrell]] \u2013 producer, engineer, and mixing {{small|(tracks 8\u201310)}}; guitar {{small|(8, 10)}}; drums {{small|(9, 10)}}; percussion, rap, and intro voice-over {{small|(8)}}; synthesizer {{small|(9)}}; bass guitar and [[mellotron]] {{small|(10)}}\n* Craig Brock \u2013 assistant guitar engineer {{small|(track 10)}}\n* [[Brad Buxer]] \u2013 keyboards {{small|(tracks 1, 7\u20139, 11)}}, synthesizer {{small|(1, 14)}}, percussion {{small|(8)}}, programming {{small|(9)}}\n* Larry Corbett \u2013 cello {{small|(track 9)}}\n* [[Andra\u00e9 Crouch]] \u2013 choir arrangements {{small|(tracks 11, 12)}}\n* [[Sandra Crouch]] \u2013 choir arrangements {{small|(tracks 11, 12)}}\n* The Andra\u00e9 Crouch Singers \u2013 choir {{small|(tracks 11, 12)}}\n* [[Heavy D]] \u2013 rap {{small|(track 1)}}\n* George Del Barrio \u2013 string arrangements {{small|(track 9)}}\n* Matt Forger \u2013 engineer and mixing {{small|(track 7)}}, engineering and sound design {{small|(8 intro)}}\n* [[Kevin Gilbert (musician)|Kevin Gilbert]] \u2013 speed sequencer {{small|(track 8)}}\n* [[Endre Granat]] \u2013 concertmaster {{small|(track 9)}}\n* Linda Harmon \u2013 soprano voice {{small|(track 9)}}\n* [[Jerry Hey]] \u2013 arrangements {{small|(track 12)}}\n* Jean-Marie Horvat \u2013 engineer {{small|(track 14)}}\n* [[Michael Jackson]] \u2013 producer and lead vocals {{small|(all tracks)}}, background vocals {{small|(1\u201312, 14)}}, arrangements {{small|(1, 9)}}, vocal arrangements {{small|(1, 3\u20137, 11, 14)}}, rhythm arrangements {{small|(7